# PDF_Viewer_Editor — .env.example
#
# Phase 1 requires NO secrets — this file is a placeholder per project-plan §2.1.
# Future phases will add cloud OCR keys, signing-cert references (Azure Key Vault),
# and telemetry endpoints here.
#
# Loaded by Diego's dev scripts via `node --env-file-if-exists=.env` (see Playbook
# entry #4 in backend-engineer.md — never use bare `--env-file` because production
# environments may not ship a .env file).

# Dev-only: Vite renderer dev-server URL. When set, main process loads from this
# URL instead of the file:// build output. Diego sets this in `npm run dev`.
# VITE_DEV_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:5173
